snippet.title: RAWMEN the Game! - Work in Progress
snippet.description:
A collection of pre-alpha footage from our multiplayer PC game RAWMEN we've been developing here at ANIMAL. Hoping to someday turn this into a reality!

Nothing is final

Music - Harry Belafonte - Jump In The Line

►Wishlist RAWMEN!
    https://store.steampowered.com/app/782940/RAWMEN/

►Follow our Twitter for up to date info
    https://twitter.com/animal_labs

►RAWMEN official site
    http://www.rawmengame.com

About ANIMAL
We're Animal — problem solvers, storytellers, artists, conceptual thinkers, and those who enjoy a damn good joke. We take pride in providing beautifully designed, well thought out and animated content to the masses; helping you connect your content to the right look'n‑balls.
